data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the perfect cul-de-sac, offering both spacious comfort and luxurious design! This magnificent residence boasts 2037 square feet of meticulously crafted living space, designed to cater to your every need. Upon entering, you are greeted by the grandeur of raised ceilings that grace both the game room and the upstairs primary bedroom. With 3 oversized bedrooms, this residence provides ample room for relaxation and privacy. Step outside onto the covered patio, an ideal space for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening. The cul-de-sac location adds an extra layer of serenity, providing a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. With its thoughtful design, meticulous attention to detail, and prime location, this residence is ready to welcome you into a lifestyle of comfort, elegance, and serenity. Brand New HVAC 10yr transferable warranty. Call Listing Agent for details and options - MOTIVATED SELLERS!! Welcome home!    *OPEN HOUSE* 1/27/24 12pm to 4pm & 1/28/24 1pm to 5pm
